Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:35.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Oh, there're mysteries and miseries
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:38.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Dead or alive　狭間に揺られて
