Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:42.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}孤独の招待　感情の消退
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:45.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}踊る1 2 3 steps on this dark stage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:47.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Raise your flag, march on, fight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:51.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}仮面の淵へ　手を掛けどただ骨が鳴るのみ
